title: stub EXE file
extract: STUB.EXE is a type of EXE file associated with Microsoft Flight Simulator 2004 A Century of Flight developed by Microsoft Game Studios for the Windows Operating System. The latest known version of STUB.EXE is 1.0.0.0, which was produced for Windows.
